comment._content: For 1914-1915 a Carl H. Keller (1875-1952), Republican was mayor of Toledo, Ohio.

comment.author: 54904823@N00
comment._content: I started a Wikipedia biography: en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carl_Henry_Keller He was born in January 9, 1875 in Ohio to John Jacob Keller and Christiana Mathias. Keller married Mame Sophia Duetscher. He was elected mayor of Toledo, Ohio in 1914 and served till 1915. He died in March 29, 1952 in Osceola County, Florida.
